blog.title: OwO Whats this??
blog.description:
Welcome to my Tumblr page! 
I'm a freelance digital artist that mainly draws character designs and sometimes fanarts, and mini comics. I'm also starting to work on a special manga with mine and my fiances characters together called "The Lovelies"! Its a pleasure meeting you guys and I can't wait to share my drawings with everyone~!! Commissions: OPEN!
If you guys are interested in one, please DM me and we can talk about it!! Icon drawn by @pinku__mochi on Instagram!
